Here is the code:
JSONObject result = json.getJSONObject("Result");
Iterator<String> iterator = result.keys();
String key;
String value;
while (iterator.hasNext()) {
    key = iterator.next();
    value = result.getString(key);
    responseView.append(key + ": " + value + "\n");
}

